DMV USA, INC., Plaintiff-Appellant, v. UNITED STATES, Defendant-Appellee. No. 02-1016. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. June 5, 2002.

Before RADER, BRYSON, and PROST, Circuit Judges.

JUDGMENT
